<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>PVP server down in final? please read.... what the hell..</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Tarquin">Tarquin</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 1:01 p.m. 15/3/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> PVP server down in final? please read.... what the hell..<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Friend told em he said that,... plus on top of that they keep saying if pvp server has less than 800-1000 people on it, they will take it down..WHY!?!! all other servers that do have less than 500 will SURELY be up (cause in future people will join them)... same thing with PVP..

<P>This is very lame from verant to do close down PVP server... I played on it most of phase 4.. It had 150 players on average, all other servers had 800+
<P>I played and it was fun , on average 10 or so players per zone (more crowded zones that is).. i can't imagine playing on a 1500 people server, thats 10x more, meaning i'd have to PUSH thro just to get to monsters... if u go in greater faydark and you see 100 people trying to kill some 20 monsters, that is going to suck big time.. iknow people will spread, but you can't go with your lv1-2 character far out... god damn it I can't believe they would close a server down.. WHAT ABOUT ALL THE PEOPLE THAT WOULD SPEND LIKE A MONTH BUILDING THEIR CHARACTERS THERE? I DO HOPE THEY REPAY OUR MONTH BILL $9.89 IF THEY DO THAT!
<P>Lemme know what you guys think
<P>-Tarquin, fighing for survival of PVP server because all other ones suck.
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
